cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

The paper proposes a deep learning model for single image dehazing, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also focuses on the efficiency and accuracy of the model, which suggests that it may belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper uses synthetic and real-world datasets, which could indicate that it belongs to the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
